The paper discusses the security of quantum cryptography, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The use of probabilistic model checking and the analysis of the BB84 protocol suggest that the paper may also fall under the categories of electronic engineering and computer science (cs.ET), information theory (cs.IT), programming languages (cs.PL), and logic in computer science (cs.LO).
